```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph External["外部应用"]
        IDE[IDE/编辑器]
        CodingAgent[编码 Agent<br/>Codex/Claude]
        CustomApp[自定义应用]
    end
    
    subgraph ACP["ACP 层"]
        ACPBridge[ACP Bridge<br/>openclaw acp]
        ACPProtocol[ACP 协议<br/>stdio/WebSocket]
    end
    
    subgraph Gateway["OpenClaw Gateway"]
        WebSocket[WebSocket 服务器<br/>:18789]
        SessionRouter[会话路由]
        AgentRuntime[Agent 运行时]
    end
    
    IDE -->|stdio| ACPBridge
    CodingAgent -->|stdio| ACPBridge
    CustomApp -->|WebSocket| ACPBridge
    
    ACPBridge -->|ACP 协议 | ACPProtocol
    ACPProtocol -->|WebSocket| WebSocket
    WebSocket --> SessionRouter
    SessionRouter --> AgentRuntime
```
